sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant LSServer as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant InlineProvider as Inline Provider<br/>(in-process)
    participant InferenceAPI as Llama Stack Inference API<br/>(in-process)
    participant DatasetIO as Llama Stack DatasetIO API<br/>(in-process)
    participant RemoteProvider as Remote Provider<br/>(in-process)
    participant KFP as Kubeflow Pipelines API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant KFPPod as KFP Pod<br/>(pipeline step)
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over Client,DatasetIO: Flow 1: Inline Evaluation
        Client->>LSServer: POST /alpha/eval/run_eval<br/>HTTP/8321
        LSServer->>InlineProvider: Route eval request
        InlineProvider->>DatasetIO: Retrieve evaluation dataset<br/>(iterrows, in-process)
        DatasetIO-->>InlineProvider: Dataset rows
        InlineProvider->>InferenceAPI: LLM completions<br/>(openai_completion, in-process)
        InferenceAPI-->>InlineProvider: Completion results
        InlineProvider->>InferenceAPI: Embeddings<br/>(openai_embeddings, in-process)
        InferenceAPI-->>InlineProvider: Embedding vectors
        Note over InlineProvider: Ragas computes metrics:<br/>answer_relevancy, context_precision,<br/>faithfulness, context_recall
        InlineProvider-->>LSServer: Evaluation scores
        LSServer-->>Client: JSON Response<br/>HTTP/8321
    end

    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
        Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: Remote Evaluation (Kubeflow Pipelines)
        Client->>LSServer: POST /alpha/eval/run_eval<br/>HTTP/8321
        LSServer->>RemoteProvider: Route eval request
        RemoteProvider->>KFP: Submit pipeline run<br/>HTTPS/443 Bearer Token
        KFP-->>RemoteProvider: Pipeline run ID
        RemoteProvider-->>LSServer: Job ID (async)
        LSServer-->>Client: Job ID response<br/>HTTP/8321

        Note over KFPPod: Step 1: Data Retrieval
        KFP->>KFPPod: Launch data retrieval pod
        KFPPod->>LSServer: GET dataset rows<br/>HTTP/8321
        LSServer-->>KFPPod: Dataset rows

        Note over KFPPod: Step 2: Ragas Evaluation
        KFP->>KFPPod: Launch evaluation pod
        KFPPod->>LSServer: LLM completions + embeddings<br/>HTTP/8321
        LSServer-->>KFPPod: Inference results
        Note over KFPPod: Ragas computes metrics
        KFPPod->>S3: Persist results (JSONL)<br/>HTTPS/443 AWS IAM
        S3-->>KFPPod: Write confirmed

        Note over Client,S3: Result Retrieval (on job_result call)
        Client->>LSServer: POST /alpha/eval/job_result<br/>HTTP/8321
        LSServer->>RemoteProvider: Get job result
        RemoteProvider->>S3: Fetch results<br/>HTTPS/443 AWS IAM
        S3-->>RemoteProvider: JSONL results
        RemoteProvider-->>LSServer: Evaluation scores
        LSServer-->>Client: JSON Response with scores<br/>HTTP/8321
    end
